, 2 inches of metal, or a thin sheet of lead blocks it. While the target is in range, the doppelganger can continue reading its thoughts, as long as the doppelganger\'s concentration isn\'t broken (as if concentrating on a spell). While reading the target\'s mind, the doppelganger has advantage on Wisdom (Insight) and Charisma (Deception, Intimidation, and Persuasion) checks against the target.---attack_bonus : 0---', '', 'http://www.dnd5eapi.co/api/monsters/86');
