reature. Hit: 2 (1d4) piercing damage plus 9 (2d8) poison damage.---attack_bonus : 6---damage_dice : 1d4---damage_bonus : 2---================================name : Longsword---desc : Melee Weapon Attack: +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 7 (1d8 + 3) slashing damage, or 8 (1d10 + 3) slashing damage if used with two hands.---attack_bonus : 6---damage_dice : 1d8---damage_bonus : 3---================================name : Longbow---desc : Ranged Weapon Attack: +6 to hit, range 150/600 ft., one target. Hit: 7 (1d8 + 3) piercing damage plus 4 (1d8) poison damage.---attack_bonus : 6---damage_dice : 1d8---damage_bonus : 3---', '', 'http://www.dnd5eapi.co/api/monsters/90');
