5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage, or 9 (2d6 + 2) piercing damage while enlarged.---attack_bonus : 4---damage_dice : 1d6---damage_bonus : 2---================================name : Invisibility (Recharges after a Short or Long Rest)---desc : The duergar magically turns invisible until it attacks, casts a spell, or uses its Enlarge, or until its concentration is broken, up to 1 hour (as if concentrating on a spell). Any equipment the duergar wears or carries is invisible with it .---attack_bonus : 0---', '', 'http://www.dnd5eapi.co/api/monsters/94');
