hin 60 feet of its summoner, acts as an ally of its summoner, and can\'t summon other mephits. It remains for 1 minute, until it or its summoner dies, or until its summoner dismisses it as an action.---attack_bonus : 0---', '', 'http://www.dnd5eapi.co/api/monsters/95');
