ne target. Hit: 10 (2d6 + 3) fire damage. If the target is a creature or a flammable object, it ignites. Until a creature takes an action to douse the fire, the target takes 5 (1d10) fire damage at the start of each of its turns.---attack_bonus : 6---damage_dice : 2d6---damage_bonus : 3---', '', 'http://www.dnd5eapi.co/api/monsters/104');
