it, range 15/30 ft., one creature. Hit: The target must make a DC 15 Constitution saving throw, taking 45 (10d8) poison damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.---attack_bonus : 8---damage_dice : 10d8---', '', 'http://www.dnd5eapi.co/api/monsters/160');
