n Attack: +9 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 13 (2d8 + 4) slashing damage.---attack_bonus : 9---damage_dice : 2d8---damage_bonus : 4---', 'name : Claw Attack---desc : The sphinx makes one claw attack.---attack_bonus : 0---================================name : Teleport (Costs 2 Actions)---desc : The sphinx magically teleports, along with any equipment it is wearing or carrying, up to 120 feet to an unoccupied space it can see.---attack_bonus : 0---================================name : Cast a Spell (Costs 3 Actions)---desc : The sphinx casts a spell from its list of prepared spells, using a spell slot as normal.---attack_bonus : 0---', 'http://www.dnd5eapi.co/api/monsters/161');
